                            <h2>Do I have to fill in a census form here?</h2>

                            <p>You should fill in an individual questionnaire here if you’re a:</p>

                            {{
                                onsList({
                                    "itemsList": [
                                        {
                                            "text": "UK resident who lives or plans to stay at the establishment for six months or more"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "text": "UK resident staying in the establishment overnight on Sunday 21 March 2021 and you have no usual residence elsewhere"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "text": "non-UK resident who lives or plans to stay in the UK for over three months and you have no other permanent UK address"
                                        }
                                    ]
                                })
                            }}

                            <p>If you’re staying in the establishment overnight on Sunday 21 March 2021 and none of these apply, you’re considered to be a visitor. The census counts visitors to establishments but asks no questions about them.</p>

                            {%
                                call onsCollapsible({
                                    "classes": 'u-mt-m',
